ygData.messageBody:
Oops, yup as soon as I sent that last one I saw it. Darn, no mention of
stackable components like fireworks and rods. Well, will have to make a run
to akanon to see what else is new. Let's hope they did more with tinkering
issues than just the cloak, but at least it's a good start. =)

Kilkin
